<part>
    <title>From the Pious People of the World</title>
    <subtitle>מ'חסידי אומות העולם - M'Chasidei Umot haOlam</subtitle>
    <partintro>
        <para><emphasis>M'Chasidei Umot haOlam</emphasis> is translated as "from the pious
            people of the world". These are people that have left their former people and have
            attached to <emphasis>Israel</emphasis>.</para>
    </partintro>
    
